{"tid":2182,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"而家啲九十後竟然打邊爐落午餐肉？？？？","createTime":"2016-11-25T18:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T12:53:47.000Z","uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f83af0bd1498d17348657f144c88837a30ac4e","tid":2182,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:30:22.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩同個九十後去打邊爐<br />\n咁我地成班就逐個寫點啲咩野食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦 到個九十後點野食<br />\n<br />\n嘩屌 我一check下張紙 屌見到有人叫午餐肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就問邊個點架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知個九十後大叫 ： 我嗌架<br />\n<br />\n我地成班同事聽到都打左個突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竟然打邊爐落午餐肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到明係午餐肉 咁點解佢要晚餐都要食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係唔係話針對幾多十後<br />\n但我肯定剩係九十後先咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84afb8a1db9c096ca0d16223b5ae1f681d8b97c","tid":2182,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:54:45.000Z","msg":"渣ga <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9265a44cef1bdab156d0b77769b1e21b8db77a","tid":2182,"uid":14230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T19:07:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b205480888b86ea4742e3d12e7996ac409a53ece","tid":2182,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:06:50.000Z","msg":"吉魯唔係到就靠你頂住啦"},{"pid":"9f21e36d4b58cf79ffbb44435a46e8f61f4e4993","tid":2182,"uid":411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:12:23.000Z","msg":"任嗌架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05253d4da85014c2fc6401e60bff7f488f3ea313","tid":2182,"uid":5355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s